additionalProperty.value: Germ Protection: Benzalkonium Chloride Cleaners: Alcohol Denat, Alkypolyglycoside (C9-C11), Propylene Glycol Butyl Ether, Ethanolamine Freshness: Fragrance Helpers: Water, Antifoam Emulsion

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Avoid contact with skin. Do not use as a baby wipe or for personal hygiene. Hard surface disinfectant only. Not to be used on skin. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If in eyes wash out immediately with a large amount of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor. Contains no phosphates.
